# Project root — paths are relative to this file (REST Client: Send Request)

### JSON: generate-answer
POST http://localhost:3000/generate-answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is an RFP?"
}

### Multipart: ask-with-file (file + question)
POST http://localhost:3000/ask-with-file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundaryJunoAskFile

------WebKitFormBoundaryJunoAskFile
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="question"

What is this document about?
------WebKitFormBoundaryJunoAskFile
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< ./juno-backend/sample.txt
------WebKitFormBoundaryJunoAskFile--
